dual X-Flash set-up
-------------------
0: on serial port
1: on USB-to-serial converter

MCA- and CCD-Acquisition Type Device Configuration

MCA-like       DEVICE   ADDR  <>MODE                                      <>TYPE
 0  YES    /dev/ttyS1     <>  115200                      Roentec XFlash MAX MCA
 1  YES  /dev/ttyUSB0     <>  115200                      Roentec XFlash MAX MCA
 2   NO
 3   NO
 4   NO
 5   NO
 6   NO
 7   NO
